<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Invoice Payment Required</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f; padding-left: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
    <h2 style="color: #d32f2f; margin: 0;">⚠ Invoice Payment Overdue</h2>
  </div>
  <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>
  <p>This is an urgent reminder that invoice <strong>#{{invoiceNumber}}</strong> for <strong>{{amount}}</strong> is now <strong>{{daysOverdue}} days overdue</strong>.</p>
  <p>Please review and authorize payment immediately to avoid service interruption.</p>
  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" style="background: #d32f2f; color: white; padding: 12px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
      Review Invoice Now
    </a>
  </div>
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">{{senderName}} | {{senderDepartment}} | {{organizationName}}</p>
</body>
</html>